|2 |└─PX COORDINATOR           |        |1       |10          |
|3 |  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX10000|1       |10          |
|4 |    └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |1       |9           |
|5 |      └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t_left  |1       |9           |
===============================================================
Outputs & filters:
