|2 |  └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |1       |7           |
|3 |    └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t_table |1       |7           |
=============================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([INTERNAL_FUNCTION(t_table.a, t_table.b)]), filter(nil), rowset=16
  1 - output([INTERNAL_FUNCTION(t_table.a, t_table.b)]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      dop=1
  2 - output([t_table.a], [t_table.b]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      force partition granule
  3 - output([t_table.a], [t_table.b]), filter([(T_OP_NOT_IN, t_table.a, (-1, 1))]), rowset=16
